name: Barbarian Canyon
description:
First Descent of this canyon completed by Scott Swaney and team 12-13-15. Could be done as a shuttle, or as a walk up and out variation (which we did). The shuttle would take too long. We missed the lower portion of this canyon, as it joins in with Monarch Canyon
